{"tid":133474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"訓唔著，又一個人落海旁坐","createTime":"2017-02-24T15:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T06:32:45.000Z","uid":50878,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76c1f1a9b6ca9ec4a87699c42f43e6cb98b51e0a","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"職場失意，情場失意<br />\n<br />\n眼見旁人一對對<br />\n自己做左咁多年人，想搵個人明白自己，鼓勵自己都好似無可能咁<br />\n幾多人唔靚仔，唔有錢，唔專一，幾人渣幾仆街既人都有人愛慕有人明白<br />\n相比自己有原則，有上進心，有良心，有正義感，<br />\n下場就幾咁淒涼<br />\n<br />\n出身低微，經歷努力，失敗，努力，失去<br />\n黎到呢個年紀，好似明白自己點都擺脫唔到命運既束搏<br />\n最慘係心入面唔甘心，有團火想改變命運，開拓未來<br />\n<br />\n好似一隻坑渠老鼠望住個天想振翅高飛咁<br />\n<br />\n最後不斷辛苦自己，重創自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚真係好凍，最好凍息我團火，等我死心"},{"pid":"8c651de2e9e2fbc9b55d7ed4da01893a7825792b","tid":133474,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"巴打咁凍仲坐海旁，小心凍親呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f644d49c04d2e150f5f38d7fce35b43e4197ee","tid":133474,"uid":37648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"巴打喺邊個海旁坐？"},{"pid":"a3c76c814091286447f9de9fa0cfe36fa7d5f1d2","tid":133474,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"我都就黎再去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9d064c2b760912cc795bfefd251506a3c2692b","tid":133474,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"好撚凍呀師父<br />\n係街飲緊啤酒都凍到震"},{"pid":"9e1d6e2b971b25baf84ee750554def1f0f47d58e","tid":133474,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"邊，度"},{"pid":"3071dca163404b8c5d6a6174ab15f5f8982d53d2","tid":133474,"uid":78571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"有咩失意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a029951c08392