b81dcab069b343a145cfeb4006f","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打咁凍仲坐海旁，小心凍親呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍死左都無人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我地攬陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHello darkness my old friend"},{"pid":"84768583dd1b675751c194fe254e8048bd3f90b6","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"每日番工做gym番工做gym咁麻醉自己等自己無力諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85800dbeaa5d5516e90b4d2ac635608236adbd1","tid":133474,"uid":87439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每一段經歷都係學習 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n小心冷親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，不過好灰，好想佢番黎，呢世都唔會遇得番咁match既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生總係充滿遺憾 剩底回憶陪住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜不是你 陪我到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67c6de1027998fc9e728002badab0e0f830639a","tid":133474,"uid":72783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有條友好唏噓咁坐佐係海旁，唔知係咪巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11256423df8c7c4587aad10ba00d702614ffbbeb","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩見到有條友好唏噓咁坐佐係海旁，唔知係咪巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成個尖咀情侶一對對，可能得我一條友自己坐係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年黎一得閒就黎坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bf03d340a4f4938198528c15deabe4273c1bc4","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一段經歷都係學習 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n小心冷親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，不過好灰，好想佢番黎，呢世都唔會遇得番咁match既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生總係充滿遺憾 剩底回憶陪住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜不是你 陪我到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人想成功<br />\n想人認同<br />\n想被愛<br />\n<br />\n深知自己一世都無緣份，剩低既只有孤單既無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a517336420747025f018dce0f16e9e24ab3e6","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CHING唔好跳海,今日凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識游水"},{"pid":"b59740223e00accdb2ff7e4fa5abb57fd121a020","tid":133474,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚凍呀師父<br />\n係街飲緊啤酒都凍到震</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，番屋企飲番杯熱水暖肚"},{"pid":"defb52264946d9c272283d5b0e0c647778b185fa","tid":133474,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CHING唔好跳海,今日凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識游水</blockquote><br />\n游水還游水, 凍還凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d337cd7e3ddc84c74bf50cb45944edf